full_text:
Compliment greetings in #morningmeeting this week.  Rendered speechless by the student who greeted me with:
"You're the reason I smile every day."
All I could say in that moment was a quiet Thank You.  Cried my eyes out later.
You never know...just sayin'
#ppspdspot https://t.co/BXhUAPaPua

full_text: My favorite line from this last section--the line that gives hope--page 175: "For the first time since we'd left the bridge, I had the feeling I'd come home." #ppspdspot
